@node "lode" "Lode Runner"

The game works but you must be sure that the CD is in the drive
(copy protection). This caused some error-messages which could be
clicked away.

Tested on:

- Amiga 4000 Rev 3.1
- CyberStorm 060/50MHz MK1
- Fastlane Z3
- CyberVision 64/4MB
- 48MB FastRAM
- 2MB ChipRAM
- Kickstart 3.0
- Workbench 3.1
- Toshiba 4x CD-ROM XM-5401TA

@endnode


@node "propin" "Pro Pinball"

