Turbo EVD gfx-driver

@endnode


@node "syndicate" "Syndicate"

Syndicate isn't very fast but it works with a resolution of 640X480.

Tested on:
- Amiga 4000
- CyberStorm 060/50MHz MK1
- Fastlane Z3
- CyberVision 64/4MB
- 48MB FastRAM
- 2MB ChipRAM
- Kickstart 3.0
- Workbench 3.1
- Toshiba 4x CD-ROM XM-5401TA

@endnode

